{"tid":1022031,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"今年我終於攞返晒以往情人節失去嘅尊嚴","createTime":"2019-02-14T16:16:56.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-14T17:48:56.000Z","uid":154769,"like":128,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"cf8a09a73cad069b1d6f7ae5102b66421e2b82e3","tid":1022031,"uid":154769,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:16:56.000Z","msg":"以往嘅情人節我都係同媽媽留係屋企過<br />\n今年終於可以過一個不一樣嘅情人節<br />\n為咗慶祝依歌不一樣嘅情人節<br />\n我特登同老細請左半日假提早返屋企預備<br />\n我沖咗個靚涼，用兩個鐘蕉咗個靚頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n着起咗好耐之前gradin淨係着過一次嘅西裝（尋晚特登叫我媽媽燙好咗俾我今日著）<br />\n就準備出門買花<br />\n臨出門前我仲攞晒床頭個月餅盒儲咗半年嘅錢出黎<br />\n同偷左我媽媽少少錢<br />\n去到樓下街市相熟嘅姨姨間花舖<br />\nolder左九十九支玫瑰<br />\n個姨姨聽完當堂擺左一個好驚訝嘅表情問我：<br />\n「阿仔，你真係要買咁多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 」<br />\n我摷一摷左自己個靚仔頭答佢：<br />\n「係啊，送比女朋友仔嘛」<br />\n之後俾咗我手上嘅全部$20同$10紙比佢<br />\n就頭也不回咁走咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我揸住紮花，啱啱好趕到係放工最多人嘅時候去到旺角<br />\n係臨落巴士之前用前置鏡頭照一照左自己個靚仔頭<br />\n就慢慢行去旺中個頭<br />\n之後我開始以一副好急嘅樣周圍穿插係人群中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n經過嘅人見到我個靚仔頭同咁大紮花<br />\n都以一副羨慕嘅眼光望著我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我知道佢地都同時羨慕緊收到依紮花嘅對象<br />\n然而其實佢地都唔知道其實我係<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">冇女嘅</span><br />\n我由5點幾扮跑扮到夜晚9點<br />\n雖然係留咗好多汗，同我個靚仔頭塔左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但係我起碼由途人同個阿姨羨慕嘅眼光<br />\n攞返依20幾年係情人節失去了尊嚴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a4296bc84f5f81c69ab8d9883d8dd46f5920f10a","tid":1022031,"uid":76105,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"做單身狗做到傻撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75cf5410cd0ac94215165f36d8689bb146c7f1e9","tid":1022031,"uid":29093,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:20:48.000Z","msg":"死gay佬"},{"pid":"f8e4d068963894b9d480bd59c83b43a5cd0612c1","tid":1022031,"uid":154769,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"a4296bc84f5f81c69ab8d9883d8dd46f5920f10a","tid":1022031,"uid":76105,"like":33,"dislike":1,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:18:43.000Z","msg":"做單身狗做到傻撚咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"真人真事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96790986e17271a57b34693396186ecd2184ae34","tid":1022031,"uid":154769,"like":16,"dislike":4,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:27:20.000Z","msg":"造型示意圖：<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CoBix48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCoBix48.png&h=0bd2fc2f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qVchODx.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqVchODx.png&h=d08d4bdf&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9HDT6qc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9HDT6qc.png&h=ed7ee56c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我係女見到都濕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aceaaff86035d43d5202294ee40b2634a7277a74","tid":1022031,"uid":231583,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:41:54.000Z","msg":"以前陪下老母做孝子咪幾好<br />\n而家痴鳩咗線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f10876a902d86a33559214ebfad57093c45af9c","tid":1022031,"uid":42414,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-14T16:59:00.000Z","msg":"創意台<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\